    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I'm not sure what to do about this issue. We can't return this as part of the JSON-RPC response, because that wouldn't be spec-compliant. And I don't think using `debug_traceTransaction` after every transaction is a good idea.\r\n\r\nMaybe we could add a [`getReturnData`](https://hardhat.org/hardhat-network-helpers/docs/overview) network helper that receives a transaction hash and returns the return data, using `debug_traceTransaction` under the hood.\r\n\r\nWhat do you think @PatrickAlphaC?",
